Name: Spoockey
About the game: SPOOCKEY is an arcade game that combines the block breaker game genre with the pace and feel of real life air hockey and some forbidden magics to create quick, thrilling PvP matches where nothing is set in stone until the very end. Features PvP air hockey-like gameplay with paddles and teleports Compete online against randos with matchmaking Challenge your friends from lobbies It turns any day into Halloween (careful with that hot PSL!) more coming in future updates... Keep an eye out and keep a cool head because it's air hockey, it's spooky... it's SPOOCKEY!!
